##### Notes

###### 1 General
    
*   This is an eprint of the River Boards Act 1908\. It incorporates all the amendments to the River Boards Act 1908 as at 10 September 2008\. The list of amendments at the end of these notes specifies all the amendments incorporated into this eprint since 3 September 2007\. Relevant provisions of any amending enactments that contain transitional, savings, or application provisions are also included, after the Principal enactment, in chronological order.

###### 2 About this eprint
    
*   This eprint has not been officialised. For more information about officialisation, please see ""Making online legislation official"" under ""Status of legislation on this site"" in the About section of this website.

###### 3 List of amendments incorporated in this eprint (most recent first)
    
*   Disability (United Nations Convention on the Rights of Persons with Disabilities) Act 2008 (2008 No 64): [section 16][180]



